          <p><em>Editor's note: A </em><a href="https://sanfordlab.org/news/photos-neutrino-day-2024"><em>version of this photo essay</em></a><em> was originally published by Sanford Underground Research Facility.</em></p>
      </div>


  </div>

</article>

